overview: Eatin' Mud!, is an actionpacked off-road adventure through the weeklong event known as the ATV Mud Nationals. Join the filthy few who dare to take on the muddiest terrain in the world! Witness the full-force mud pit action. Featuring mud bog madness, deep water mud-a-cross, big air quad freestyle, and mud slingin' on the edge of insantiy.
title: Eatin' Mud
